subtitleNullable: A dataset consisiting of 250k Hangul characters with labels.
descriptionNullable: A dataset consisting of 265550 images of Hangul characters with mapped labels. Each image is 224x224 pixels. The 2350 most frequent characters derived from the KS X 1001 encoding were used to create the images. This dataset can be used for computer vision and multimodel NLP/transformers. It will be used to train multiple different Vision Transformers for Hangul Recognition. Trained models will be released. This dataset is based on an outdated repository by IBM: https://github.com/IBM/tensorflow-hangul-recognition.
